            "title": "盤中速報 - 櫃買市場加權指數上漲7.39點至254.09點，漲幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間20日09:10，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲7.39點（或3%），暫報254.09點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-4.68%</li><li>近 1 月：-6.29%</li><li>近 3 月：-0.11%</li><li>近 6 月：+8.64%</li><li>今年以來：-2.37%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普稅改概念領漲+4.26%。其中    IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)            上漲        7.81%            ;        台化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>)            上漲        4.1%            ;        台塑(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>)            上漲        3.25%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>車用PCB概念領漲+4.03%。其中    精成科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6191:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6191\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6191-TW</a>)            上漲        7.69%            ;        高技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5439:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5439\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5439-TW</a>)            上漲        5.39%            ;        楠梓電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2316-TW</a>)            上漲        5.17%    。</p></section></main>",
